  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1058">
<l>irappārai yillāyi ṉīrṅkaṇmā ñāla </l>
<l>marappāvai ceṉṟuvan taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If there were no beggars, (the actions done in) the cool wide world would only resemble the movement of a puppet.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
